{
  "stem": "9446.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "On the other hand, this caused the Jews to isolate themselves from the rest of the population, from the Poles.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they-- they never quite became-- the majority of the Jewish people-- we're talking about three million people in Poland-- three million Jews-- never quite became part of the Polish society.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Anti-Semitism is one reason.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The other reason is-- see, it is a story with-- sometimes, you can compare this with the chicken and an egg.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Nobody knows what started first.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because of anti-Semitism, Jews isolated themselves, and they had to seek other ways of survival, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They couldn't get a lot of jobs which the Poles where able to get.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they turned to commerce, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Many Poles became terribly anti-Semitic, because when they saw 1 or 2 or 10 Jews  who were maybe dishonest, they branded, automatically, all the Jews being crooks.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know what I mean?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's the story.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We suffered with this for years, through generations.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's why I don't like people who say, all the Poles are anti-Semites, because that's just as stupid as-- as the Poles who say all the Jews are crooks.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's not such-- and even among Germans, there were some Germans who were decent, believe it or not.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So one can not put everybody in the same.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's just unfair, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jews in Germany enjoyed all the freedoms.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As a  matter of fact, Jews in Germany felt much better about themselves than the Jews in Poland felt about themselves.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the Germans being not Catholic but Protestant, you know, Protestant religion is, in quite substantial ways, different from Catholics.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so far as the Jews are concerned, the Protestants were much friendlier to Jews than the Catholics ever were.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
